{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, F ℘ satisfies (6.14).Next, suppose F ℘ satisfies (6.14), and consider x, y, z ∈ W with xR δ y and xR α z.",
    "Then setting X = {x} and Y = {y}, there is a X ′ ⊑ X for which the rest of (6.14) holds.",
    "Now X ′ ⊑ X = {x} implies X ′ = {x}.",
    "Then since xR α z gives us {x}R α {z}, setting Z = {z} in (6.14) gives us a U ̸ = ∅ such that {y}R γ U and {z}R β U, which implies there is a u ∈ U such that yR γ u and zR β u.",
    "Thus, F satisfies (6.13)."
  ]
}